aa(lp76
VBut the worst part was,
p77
aVnot the spontaneous pain that was there 24 hours a day.
p78
aVThe worst part was that she had allodynia,
p79
aVthe medical term for the phenomenon that I just illustrated
p80
aVwith the feather and with the torch.
p81
aVThe lightest touch of her arm \u2014
p82
aVthe touch of a hand,
p83
aVthe touch even of a sleeve, of a garment, as she put it on \u2014
